Some things to see if you have a Westfakia..a transporter converted to a
camper:

No jalousie windows
vinyl headliner
vinyl behind the driver's seats

 These things can be added removed though.

Some Riviera's etc, had the vinyl, but they were all pop tops as far as I
know.

